Package: expranno
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight Annotation-First RNA-Seq Workflows
Version: 3.0.0
Author: Dai [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Dai <daik54015@gmail.com>
Description: Provides a minimal downstream RNA-seq workflow for expression
    matrices whose first column is Ensembl gene identifiers and metadata
    tables whose first column is sample identifiers. The package annotates
    human or mouse genes, merges annotated expression with metadata, and can
    optionally run deconvolution and GSVA or ssGSEA signature scoring when
    the required backends are installed.
